Phase 5 Tasks 1-2: Cursor Rendering

Files changed:
  - src/renderer/cursor.rs (NEW): CursorState, CursorStyle, flag constants, blink timer
  - src/renderer/mod.rs: added cursor submodule
  - src/renderer/gpu.rs: added PartialEq derive to CellInstance

Implementation:
  - CursorStyle enum: Block, Beam, Underline
  - CursorState manages position, style, focus, blink timer
  - Flag encoding: bit 1=is_cursor, bits 2-3=shape (block/beam/underline/hollow)
  - Blink interval: 500ms toggle via Instant-based timer
  - Unfocused window shows hollow block cursor regardless of style
  - to_cell_instance() generates CellInstance with cursor colors and flags

Tests (25 new, 227 total):
  - Cursor position: origin, update, default style/visible/focused (5)
  - Block cursor: generates instance, position, flag, shape, colors (5)
  - Beam cursor: shape flag, cursor flag (2)
  - Underline cursor: shape flag, cursor flag (2)
  - Hollow block: unfocused shows hollow, still has cursor flag, refocus restores style (3)
  - Blink timing: initially visible, not-visibleâ†’None, toggle, no-change-before-interval, off/on (6)
  - Set style: beam, underline (2)

